longBusinessSummary: Sheen Tai Holdings Group Company Limited, an investment holding company, generates and sells photovoltaic power in Hong Kong and Mainland China. The company operates in four segments: Sales of Sub-processing Cigarette Films; Properties Development and Related Services; Generation of Photovoltaic Power; and Sales of semi-conductors. The company is also involved in the trading of sub-processed cigarette films; trading of semi-conductors; development and sale of properties; provision of property management services; printing of cigarette films; and agriculture technology business. Sheen Tai Holdings Group Company Limited was founded in 1997 and is based in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.
